                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#5r">5r</locus> (incipit page of Text I): coloured (red, blue
                        and black) ornamental band; interlaces and floral motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2">
                        <locus target="#9v">Fol. 9v: </locus>
