                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#127va">ff. 127va-128</locus>
                           <desc>ra: ʾAsmat-prayer.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#127va">127va</locus>: በስመ፡ አብወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወትብል፡
                              በትሑት፡ ቃል፡ እሎንተ፡ አስማተ፡ ዓቢያተ... [<locus target="#127vb">127vb</locus>]... እሉ፡ ክቡራን፡ አስማቲሁ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ዘተረክቡ፡ በእደ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡
                              ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀረ፡ ወጸላዕት።...</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The prayer is written by the same hand as the main text. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Omissions inserted interlineally: e.g., <locus target="#7vb">7vb</locus>, 9rb, 44vb, 67ra. 
 - Corrections
