                           [several lines], 46va. 
 - Tamallas-sign (in the shape of +)
                           indicating the place where the omission, written in the bottom margin,
                           belong: <locus target="#81va">81va</locus>. 
 - Crude drawings and
                           scribbles: <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 2r, 130r, 131v.</item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc type="findingAid">- Monthly readings are indicated by the names of the
                              months written in the upper margin, in red or black: ዘታኅሳስ፡ <locus target="#19ra">fol. 19ra</locus> ዘጥር፡ <locus target="#28vb">fol.
                                 28vb</locus> ዘመጋቢት፡ <locus target="#49va">fol. 49va</locus> ዘሚያዝያ:
                                 <locus target="#73ra">fol. 73ra</locus> ዘግንቦት: <locus target="#81va">fol. 81va</locus> ዘሰኔ: <locus target="#86va">fol.
                                 86va</locus> ዘሐምሌ: <locus target="#103vb">fol. 103vb</locus> The
                              indications for the months ሕዳር, የካቲት, መስከረም and ጥቅምት are
                              missing.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
